This paper deals with natural language processing and machine translation, which are closely related to the sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). The use of surface expressions and examples to recover omitted verbs involves the use of machine learning algorithms, which falls under the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval and text mining, which are related to the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the use of examples to recover omitted verbs involves the use of neural networks, which falls under the sub-category of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
